    <p class="text-lg">Here in this members-only lounge, we celebrate the joyful chaos of Tinky Winky, Dipsy, Laa-Laa, and Po with <strong>exclusive treats</strong> that non-members can only dream of. Get ready to tubby your way through special content and community bonding!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 text-center">ðŸŽ‰ What Awaits You in Our Whimsical Wonderland? ðŸŽ‰</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-100 to-yellow-100 p-6 rounded-2xl border-4 border-pink-300">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Exclusive Fan Art Gallery</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">Browse stunning, member-submitted artwork inspired by the Teletubbies' colorful adventures. From pastel sketches of Baby Sun to vibrant scenes in Teletubbyland</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 to-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-paint-brush text-white text-2xl"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-green-100 p-6 rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-300">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Behind-the-Scenes Content</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">Access exclusive videos, interviews, and never-before-seen moments from the Teletubbies universe. See the magic happen behind the scenes!</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-green-400 flex items-center justify-center">
